<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shén de diàn huāng liáng 迦南352</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shén de diàn huāng liáng shǒu wàng de rén zài nǎ lǐ,
 chéng qiáng tān tā gè rén zhuān gù zì jǐ, zhǔ xīn yōu shāng zhǔ xīn jiāo jí,
 duì zhǔ zuǐ shàng dōu mǎn le ài qíng xīn què yǔ zhǔ yuǎn lí,
 shéi néng wèi zhǔ zhàn qǐ, dōu xiǎng tuì hòu táo bì, zhēn xīn fù chū de rén zài nǎ lǐ.
 lèi shuǐ dī luò yī shān, yī shān mǎn le lèi dī,
 yǒu rén sǐ zài zuì lǐ, yǒu rén hái zài āi jí, zhǔ a qiú nǐ xìng qǐ xìng qǐ.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>352</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>